The '''Croatian Film Archive''' ({{lang-hr|Hrvatska kinoteka}}) is the national film archive of [[Croatia]]. It is a member of the [[International Federation of Film Archives]]<ref>[http://www.fiafnet.org/uk/members/Directory_.cfm International Federation of Film Archives Membership Information] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409002002/http://www.fiafnet.org/uk/members/Directory_.cfm |date=2009-04-09 }}</ref> and of ACE, the [[Association of European Film Archives and Cinematheques]]. The archive was founded in 1979.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hda.arhiv.hr/hr/novosti/pregled/razno/2009/kinoteka/index.html|title=Obilježavanje 30. GODIŠNJICE RADA HRVATSKE KINOTEKE i SVJETSKOG DANA AUDIOVIZUALNE BAŠTINE|publisher=[[Croatian State Archives]]|accessdate=2012-01-19}}</ref>
